title: Amy’s Burglary Scare + Throwback Thursday With Clint Black + Favorite 90’s Country Songs + Arkansas Keith's Top Three Fish To Eat
itunes:title: Amy’s Burglary Scare + Throwback Thursday With Clint Black + Favorite 90’s Country Songs + Arkansas Keith's Top Three Fish To Eat
description:
Amy shares drama from her house last night as she thought she woke up to a burglar at 2 a.m. We celebrate 'Throwback Thursday' with special guest Clint Black. He talks about his biggest 90’s hits, being named one of 'People' magazine's sexiest people and 'The Apprentice'. Plus, Arkansas Keith joins us for some fish talk!
